        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Sap Vitality</em></p>\n<p>You draw the willpower from a creature you can see within range. Make a ranged force attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes 2d6 necrotic damage and it deals only half damage with weapon attacks that use Strength until the power ends.</p>\n<p>At the end of each of the target&rsquo;s turns, it can make a Constitution saving throw against the power. On a success, the power ends.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Force Potency.</strong></em>&nbsp;When you cast this power using a force slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 2nd.</p>",
